title: Elon Musk Won’t Pay His Taxes & Joe Rogan Hates Paternity Leave - Leftovers #6
description: On this episode of Leftovers we learn that concrete can be grown on trees, that January 6th was a antifa false flag operation, that Joe Rogan can't fathom fathers wanting to spend time with their newborns, and Biden's "Build Back Better" bill transforms into a "Somewhat Better" bill!
